-is-completely-unfair-3844381">Lady Gaga explains support for trans community: “What trans people are being faced with in this world is completely unfair”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lady Gaga is seen signing autographs. Credit - Getty Images/MEGA/GC Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> has explained why she spoke up for the trans community during her Grammy Award acceptance speech <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-hail-trans-people-and-perform-california-dreamin-with-bruno-mars-in-honour-of-la-at-2025-grammys-3833966">last month</a> .</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga-chromatica-album-review-2677590">Lady Gaga  - “色彩”评论：来自她自己的世界中的图标纯流行音乐庆典</a></strong></li></ul><p>Gaga and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruno-mars">Bruno Mars</a> picked up the Best Pop Duo/Group Performance award for their collaboration &#39;Die With A Smile&#39;, which <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-hail-trans-people-and-perform-california-dreamin-with-bruno-mars-in-honour-of-la-at-2025-grammys-3833966">saw Gaga send a message of support</a> to the trans community while accepting the Grammy.</p><p> She said at the time: “I just want to say tonight that trans people are not invisible.跨性别者应该得到爱。酷儿社区值得抬高。音乐是爱。谢谢。” </p><figure id="attachment_3834166" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834166" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834166" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_ladygaga_brunomars_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_ladygaga_brunomars_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_ladygaga_brunomars_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_ladygaga_brunomars_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_ladygaga_brunomars_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_ladygaga_brunomars_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_ladygaga_brunomars_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834166" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars speak onstage during the 67th Annual GRAMMY Awards at on February 2, 2025 in Los Angeles CREDIT: Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for The Recording Academy</figcaption></figure><p> On March 5, the musician was interviewed by DJ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zane-lowe">Zane Lowe</a> for <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ts-r3J0uqdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple Music</a> and spoke about why she is such a vocal trans ally. Gaga said she believes trans people must be “protected” from anti-trans laws that US president Donald Trump is trying to push through.</p><p> “What I would say first and foremost is what trans people are being faced with in this world is completely unfair, wrong, and there&#39;s this violence that&#39;s taking place on a daily basis in their lives,” Gaga explained.</p><p> “I think that we all need to support trans people and each other to know that they deserve to be supported and loved and protected and lifted up.</p><p> “What I go through in my life is very different from that, and what every community that is oppressed goes through is different, it&#39;s all unique experience. And then there&#39;s individual people, and everyone&#39;s individual experience is different.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lady Gaga：Zane Lowe采访" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ts-r3J0uqdk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Gaga also shared that one of the greatest things she learned is to take time to understand people&#39;s stories and backgrounds, which has made her a better ally to the trans community.</p><p> Elsewhere in the interview, the musician spoke about ageism in the music industry, and how she was unsure if she would be “accepted” despite only being 38. “I ultimately decided that a woman could be powerful at any age,” she told Lowe.</p><p> The singer&#39;s highly anticipated seventh album &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-new-album-mayhem-3832317">Mayhem</a> &#39; is out today (March 7).从2020年代的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga-chromatica-album-review-2677590">“色彩”</a>和她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-joker-2-companion-album-harlequin-3796692"><em>Joker：Folie：Deux</em> Companion唱片“ Harlequin”</a>之后，该唱片于去年发行。</p><p> In her interview with Lowe, Gaga has explained how the LP sits in her discography and the different approach she has taken with it compared to her previous albums.</p><p> In other news, Gaga is set to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-to-celebrate-mayhem-release-by-pulling-double-duty-on-snl-3839233">pull double duty on <em>Saturday Night Live</em> (SNL) on March 8, after &#39;Mayhem&#39;&#39;s launch</a> , where she will host the long-running sketch show and perform as a musical guest.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-explains-support-for-trans-community-what-trans-people-are-being-faced-with-in-this-world-is-completely-unfair-3844381">Lady Gaga explains support for trans community: “What trans people are being faced with in this world is completely unfair”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
